 9. 1899</date> achtzig.</note><space unit="chars" quantity="5"/> Arthur S.</p><p>Dies wünschen Ihnen</p><closer><signed>Richard</signed><lb/><signed><handShift scribe="#pmb11740"/>Hugo</signed></closer></div></body><back><listPerson><person xml:id="pmb11740">
